content: Purchased this once; it's still on my account but I can't upgrade to this version (the only difference is supporting the newest version of Android) without paying for it a second time. Also, keep in mind that you have to pay for this game on every device you want to install it on. I loved this company and their stories but this is a despicable business practice.

Backlog history is the most important part of visual novel and you have no option for that? I will rate this by 2 star for now until this game adds backlog if you can add it I will rate this to 5 stars
Absolutely amazing. Though was there supposed to be an opening trailer, because when I open the app, it just takes me straight to the main menu screen.
Love the story, characters and art. Loved it so much I have both on my computer and phone. Love the work PixelFade does. Have all their games.
